{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_21191.jpg","bgm":"bgm01_anime02","chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":100104,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"","narration":"[se:7106_telmail]Jingle♪","narrationBg":"","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":100104,"motion":401}],"nameCenter":"Iroha","narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"Ah...!"},{"chara":[{"id":100104,"motion":0}],"nameNarration":"Rabi","narration":"Dear members of the Kamihama Magia Union,@Promised Blood, the Tokime Clan,@and the Neo-Magius,","narrationBg":"","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"This is a reminder that, as stated in our@recent meeting, Professor Satomi and I will be@hosting our presentation on Yukuni and@Folklore of Zero at 9:00 am today."},{"narration":"The presentation will take place at the@Kamihama Aquarium as originally planned.@Do note, however, that the entrance is at the@Marine Biology Institute located at the rear@of the building, rather than the front door."},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_21031.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":102101,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"","narration":"[se:7106_telmail]Jingle♪","narrationBg":"","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":102101,"motion":300}],"nameCenter":"Yuna","narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"...Hmm?"},{"chara":[{"id":102101,"motion":1}],"nameCenter":"Yuna","textCenter":"...Well then, I guess we need to get ready to head@out."},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_15111.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102501,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102701,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"","narration":"[se:7106_telmail]Jingle♪","narrationBg":"","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":102501,"motion":400}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","narrationEffect":"out","textLeft":"Hmmm?! There's a strange sound coming from my@phone...!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102701,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Sunao","textRight":"This is normal, remember."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102501,"motion":100,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Shizuka","textLeft":"Oh right, I received a message just now,@didn't I?"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_14121.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":103900,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":104100,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":103900,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Sudachi","textRight":"...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":104100,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"Livia","textLeft":"What's up, is something wrong?"},{"chara":[{"id":103900,"motion":100}],"nameRight":"Sudachi","textRight":"...Fumumumumumumumu..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":104000,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Yozuru","textRight":"She said, \"There's a gathering at the Kamihama@Aquarium.\""},{"chara":[{"id":104100,"motion":100}],"nameLeft":"Livia","textLeft":"A gathering?"},{"chara":[{"id":104000,"motion":1}],"nameRight":"Yozuru","textRight":"I've heard word about it as well."},{"chara":[{"id":104000}],"nameRight":"Yozuru","textRight":"Apparently, it's an invitation from Folklore of Zero."},{"chara":[{"id":104000,"motion":300}],"nameRight":"Yozuru","textRight":"I heard that representatives of the main groups are@gathering."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":104100,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Livia","textLeft":"...Heh~"},{"chara":[{"id":104100,"motion":400}],"nameLeft":"Livia","textLeft":"Well then, why don't I go and@show my face for a bit...!"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_21146.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102801,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"","narration":"[se:7106_telmail]Jingle♪","narrationBg":"","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":102801}],"nameCenter":"Himena","narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"...I thought it was about time..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":102801,"motion":200,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Himena","textCenter":"Well then, let's go, Hiko."},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"black","bgm":"stop","item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/part2_chapter11_another/208101_aruchang.png","posX":0,"posY":-70,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"charaBack"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm20_song10","nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<Thus, the situation started moving again...>","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<At this point, Kagome had...>"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<...already decided to make a@contract as a Magical Girl.>"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<However, there was one problem...> "},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<She was asking herself,@\"What should I do with my wish?\">"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<And as the situation unfolded, so did her wish...>"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_19332.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0},{"id":810000,"motion":0,"pos":0,"posX":-50,"posY":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"blackFrame"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":400}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"So please, make my wish come true!","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":810000,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"Kyubey","textLeft":"...!!"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":1}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"I want..."},{"chara":[{"id":102001}],"nameNarration":"Kagome","narration":"\"Kyubey, I want the power to make you@and your kind unable to interfere with@the Automatic Purification System forever!\"","narrationEffect":"in"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"black","item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/part2_chapter11_another/208101_aruchang.png","posX":0,"posY":-70,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"charaBack"}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<This is the conclusion she came to...>","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<I think there was a specific event@that led her to this.>"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<That would be...>"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"black","item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/part2_chapter8/102909_toka_nemu1.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"blackFrame"},{"nameNarration":"Touka","narration":"―Touka―@If we transform into Magical Girls,@these bracelets will explode.","narrationAnchor":"bottom","narrationCoverOpacity":110.0,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationFontSize":30.0,"narrationLineMargin":35.0,"narrationLineSpace":20.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"narration":"―Touka―@That's the punishment we received for committing so many evils,@even going so far as sacrificing Kamihama City and the Feathers."},{"nameNarration":"Nemu","narration":"―Nemu―@And yet, today we dare to take that punishment@and channel it into hope."},{"narration":"―Nemu―@Together, as our atonement as Magius..."},{"nameNarration":"Nemu & Touka","narration":"―Nemu & Touka―@We will now save Magical Girls!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"flashEffect":"explosion","item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/part2_chapter8/102909_toka_nemu2.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear"}],"narrationEffect":"out","se":"7205_magic_girl","turnEffect":"promist"},{"nameNarration":"Touka","narration":"―Touka―@If the Eternal Sakura over there is still alive,@it means our first phase was a success!","narrationAnchor":"bottom","narrationCoverOpacity":110.0,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationFontSize":30.0,"narrationLineMargin":10.0,"narrationLineSpace":20.0},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"bg":"white","narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"whiteIn"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"jingle":"1023D14"},{"autoTurnLast":1.5,"jingle":"1004D20"},{"nameNarration":"Kagome","narration":"[textRed:\"KYAAAAAAAAAAHH!!\"]","narrationCoverOpacity":0.0,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationFontSize":40.0,"turnChangeOut":"whiteOut"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"black","item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/part2_chapter11_another/208101_aruchang.png","posX":0,"posY":-70,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"charaBack"}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<That incident left a deep scar on Kagome's@heart...>","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<In a way, I think it's fair to say@that a curse was placed upon her.>"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<As I've said before, Kagome is@a girl who finds her resolve.>"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<After witnessing the sacrifice of those two,@as expected, Kagome...>"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<She was prepared to put herself on the line too...>"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<That resolve is reflected in Kagome's wish.>"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<Kagome has changed...>"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<Every time she found her resolve, she changed...>"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<Even since before she became a Magical Girl, Kagome...>"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<has always been \"transforming\", all along.>"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<Over and over again...>"},{"nameCenter":"Aru","textCenter":"<And that's...>"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"whiteIn"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"turnChangeOut":"whiteOut"},{"chara":[{"id":102001}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"Something that I think will@continue into the future..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":102001}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"New resolve will surely change me..."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
